{"tid":1380073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反修例】王婆婆慨嘆回歸後三權分立受破壞 籲年輕人雖辛苦但冀堅持到最後","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T03:02:29.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af44b9ac857452ae3dbe99a70007302530d41095","tid":1380073,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"反修例的遊行自二月開始，近兩個月幾乎每個周末也有遊行或集會，即使政府道歉仍未能平息民憤，沒有人知道這場「持久戰」會直至何時。63歲王婆婆形容好辛苦，但呼籲年輕人要堅持到最後。<br />\n<br />\n王婆婆表示，今次年輕人在網上的策略可算是成功，政府現時是「唔知點算」。她指雖然辛苦，但希望年輕人可以繼續爭取，堅持到最後。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被問及高舉英國旗的原因，王婆婆憶述當年被英國統治時、香港未回歸前，作為港人是「完全睇到香港有前途」：只係借番嚟嘅地方，但都用心建設。雖然並唔係完美，冇政府係完美嘅。</span><br />\n<br />\n年輕時曾於維也納讀書和居住，王婆婆慨嘆回歸後，香港的醫療系統、教育制度、三權分立等核心價值備受破壞和蠶食；而2016年起DQ（撤銷）立法會議員資格，更是不可接受。<br />\n<br />\n至於現時香港猶如一個「困局」，她認為要立即實行雙普選，雖然心知政府是不會接受，或是可先循取消功能組別著手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2412828/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2412828%2F&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67WXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=e9313adf\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2412828/</a>"},{"pid":"e3e7237813260d0a6590ad306a45a3c041dbc300","tid":1380073,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DnvCvEX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDnvCvEX.jpg&h=94f21ac2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1b6cc9241618bc0312e98b38f004793dc0820e7","tid":1380073,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"王婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4688880cf58185453101b457a2af43c9ebac86d8","tid":1380073,"uid":200532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:32:13.000Z","msg":"婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da32c483cb4484f93ca23e82fc146ce3c0a30bb","tid":1380073,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Drm6o0Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrm6o0Q.jpg&h=36708533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7VUWMea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7VUWMea.png&h=dbfbb77b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6edf170bb217454d2000ed3dd5bbc001e4c2cd7b","tid":1380073,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6410c5ff29c90c1c79542ab1942f9f340fc89a","tid":1380073,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}